This paper is likely to belong to the cs.AI sub-category as it deals with a fundamental AI reasoning method, Abductive reasoning. It may also belong to cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) as it discusses the computational complexity of Abduction. Additionally, the paper utilizes structural properties of the problem, which may make it relevant to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity). Finally, the paper presents fixed-parameter tractable transformations, which may make it relevant to cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics).
